leadership-approach|vision_results_process_people|strength_1|1|A stronger frame for change|When this pattern is working well, Vision gives leadership a wider frame. People can see why the work matters, what future consequence is involved, and why the current choice deserves attention.|vision|active|leadership-approach::vision_results_process_people::strength_1
leadership-approach|vision_results_process_people|strength_2|2|Direction that reaches a decision|Vision and Results together can connect possibility to ownership. The strength is that future thinking is less likely to stay high-level because it is pulled towards a decision, outcome, or next step.|results|active|leadership-approach::vision_results_process_people::strength_2
leadership-approach|vision_results_process_people|strength_3|3|Range through stronger trust after Process|Process can broaden the first two signals before People is brought in deliberately. People adds range when the pattern has movement, structure, or direction and now needs better communication around the human impact. It can make progress more sustainable because people understand their part in the work.|people|active|leadership-approach::vision_results_process_people::strength_3
