leadership-approach|vision_process_people_results|strength_3|3|Range through firmer ownership after People|People can broaden the first two signals before Results is brought in deliberately. Results adds range when the pattern has already created trust, structure, or direction and now needs a clearer decision. It can turn good leadership intent into ownership, visible movement, and follow-through.|results|active|leadership-approach::vision_process_people_results::strength_3
